com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=bb9a422c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"根據2019年《香港人權法案》的要求，香港人現在將此提議作為2020年香港普選計劃。<br />\n1.將區議會修改為眾議院，將議會修改為參議院。<br />\n2.參議院議員需要眾議院建議，並由有效選民選舉產生。<br />\n3.將行政長官升任總理。<br />\n4.總理應由有效選民選出。<br />\n5.取消總理的年齡和國籍限制。<br />\n6.修改對香港人而不是對中華人民共和國的忠誠承諾。<br />\n7.取消人大對香港人擁有的《基本法》的解釋和修改的權力。<br />\n8.廢除中聯辦和人大常委會的政治能力和影響。<br />\n9.公民動議權和法律修改權應得到保障。<br />\n10.議會對議員的彈劾為總議員數60％（兩者）"},{"pid":"5713bf380e88c45bdb620597d7b72f7ec68e8e9b","tid":1808733,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b3ecb6f72177ab0e3d8b3bf06c465b7f790c4e","tid":1808733,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c35e59b7d217697ba85e295d1ebaec81fdf2eec3","tid":1808733,"uid":75655,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZjB1Da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZjB1Da.jpg&h=0a7cb33e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"支那memes<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"咪幾夾d捉鬼撚"},{"pid":"05c40b7977c9d423f9e2da0912683a78cf89bf9e","tid":1808733,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鬼裝修割唔割？係咪對家計謀？且看割唔割席兩步曲，教你睇穿風向背後更深層嘅陰謀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809005</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>大家快ｄ去簽，叫埋其他人簽<br />\n2020年雙普選聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=bb9a422c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>根據2019年《香港人權法案》的要求，香港人現在將此提議作為2020年香港普選計劃。<br />\n1.將區議會修改為眾議院，將議會修改為參議院。<br />\n2.參議院議員需要眾議院建議，並由有效選民選舉產生。<br />\n3.將行政長官升任總理。<br />\n4.總理應由有效選民選出。<br />\n5.取消總理的年齡和國籍限制。<br />\n6.修改對香港人而不是對中華人民共和國的忠誠承諾。<br />\n7.取消人大對香港人擁有的《基本法》的解釋和修改的權力。<br />\n8.廢除中聯辦和人大常委會的政治能力和影響。<br />\n9.公民動議權和法律修改權應得到保障。<br />\n10.議會對<strong>總理</strong>的彈劾為總議員數60％（兩者）</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3d31b020dcd91d536417039bc8978ce8d23ded60","tid":1808733,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"捉鬼都係前線做啦幾時輪到班和理非"}]}